{"word":"κερδαίνω","slug":"κερδαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰερδαίνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κέρδος\">κέρδος</a></el>] <b>gain<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as mercantile term for profitable investment <b><a href='B:470 16:26'>Mt 16:26</a>; <a href='B:470 25:16'>25:16f</a>; <a href='B:660 4:13'>Js 4:13</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> by extension of a:<b> <a href='B:470 18:15'>Mt 18:15</a>; <a href='B:530 9:19-22'>1 Cor 9:19-22</a>; <a href='B:570 3:8'>Phil 3:8</a>; <a href='B:670 3:1'>1 Pt 3:1</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> in irony <b><a href='B:510 27:21'>Ac 27:21</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κεράτιον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κερδάνω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}